Cyberpunk style: A towering fortress made of glowing amber hexagonal honeycomb structures stands resilient in a dark digital landscape, while streams of malicious red code and data packets rain down from a stormy neon-lit sky, bouncing harmlessly off its protective geometric shell. The fortress emits a warm golden light from within, contrasting against the hostile purple and red cyber-storm swirling around it. Fractured SQL symbols and corrupted data fragments scatter and dissolve upon contact with the amber barrier. In the foreground, sleek chrome cables and circuit pathways lead toward the protected structure like roads to a safe haven. The atmosphere is tense yet hopeful, with electric blue lightning crackling in the distance and holographic shields rippling with each deflected attack.
